def has_plug_and_switch(cd_player:item):
    # Check if the CD player has a plug and a switch
    return has_plug(cd_player) and has_switch(cd_player)

behavior plug_in_cd_player(cd_player:item, power_socket:item):
    body:
        achieve plugged(cd_player)

behavior switch_on_cd_player(cd_player:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(cd_player)

behavior __goal__():

        bind power_socket: item where:
            is_powersocket(power_socket)
        if has_plug_and_switch(cd_player):
            plug_in_cd_player(cd_player, power_socket)
            switch_on_cd_player(cd_player)
